# auto-api-java — Java client for auto-api.com

- Java 11+, only dependency: Gson
- java.net.http.HttpClient (built-in)
- Single AutoApiClient class, 6 synchronous methods
- Fluent builder pattern for OffersParams
- @SerializedName for snake_case JSON mapping
- Unchecked exceptions (extends RuntimeException)
- JsonElement for raw offer data — varies between sources
- Javadoc on every public type and method, in English
- ApiException for API errors, AuthException for 401/403

## Key Files

- src/main/java/com/autoapi/client/AutoApiClient.java — main client
- src/main/java/com/autoapi/client/model/ — data models
- src/main/java/com/autoapi/client/exception/ — exception classes
- build.gradle — project configuration

## Never

- Add more dependencies beyond Gson
- Use checked exceptions
- Use Lombok
- Write comments or docs in non-English languages
